## **10-1 How to get started with CT?**

* Obtain a CT account, go here: [https://ct.nmrsolutions.io/](https://ct.nmrsolutions.io/)  

* Familiarize yourself with the software and take a tour at [CT Support:](https://helpy.nmrsolutions.fi/en)

  * Analysis Dashboard or “Home page”, it is represented by the house icon in the following image on the top right corner: ![][image1]Spectrum name  
    ![][image2]

  * Data Manager & Import or “Server page”, it is represented by the three circular disc icon in the previous image on the top right corner: ![][image3]![][image4]  
    

  * Analysis window (once you open a case): with the eye icon in view mode, with the pencil icon in edit mode.  
    ![][image5]
